metadata.title: Marbled Murrelets Aerial Telemetry
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  Aerial telemetry locations for 47 radio tagged marbled murrelets tracked during the 1994 field season.  Database record of survey observations. Data intended for research and management purposes.
